documents: From 2023-08-08 to 2026-04-01, temporary stop closures affected routes 700, 753, 754, 757, 765, and 777 on Gold Coast Highway, including locations like Nobby Beach, Mermaid Beach, Annette Kellerman Park, Burleigh Heads, Christine Avenue, and Miami due to Gold Coast Light Rail works.

From 2023-09-25 5:00 AM to early 2026, the footpath between Woolloongabba station platform 2 and Main Street is closed due to Cross River Rail construction. Access to platform 2 is via Stanley Street pedestrian overpass with stairs and a lift. During major Gabba events, an additional footpath will be available.

On 09/10/2023, temporary stop closures affected routes 600, 611, and 615 at Brisbane Road, Mooloolaba Bowls Club due to issues with bus travel along Foote Street. Use alternative stops: Walan Street near Bahlaka Street (Stop ID 301709) and Mooloolaba, River Esplanade (Stop ID 301708).
From 2024-03-03 1:00 AM to 2025-12-31, platform changes at Broadbeach South station require using platform 2 near Gold Coast Highway. No changes to tram times or local bus services.

From 02/02/2026 7:45 PM to 28/02/2026 4:00 AM, evening weekday Shorncliffe Line services between Northgate and Shorncliffe stations are suspended during track closures. Railbus R348 replaces trains between these stations, stopping at all stations, with 30-minute intervals. Bikes and e-scooters are prohibited on railbuses. Weekend travel may also be impacted.

From 2024-12-09 5:00 AM to mid-2026, Salisbury station and the overpass bridge between Dollis Street and Lillian Avenue are closed for Cross River Rail upgrade works. Alternative services include StationLink route 19, routes 110, 115, and 117 from Beaudesert Road. Rocklea and Coopers Plains stations offer accessible options during the closure.
From 2025-01-26 to 2025-06-30, temporary stop closures on Drews Road near Piari Street affected routes 553, 565, and school services. Use the alternative stop on Drews Road near Barokee Drive.
From 2025-05-16 2:00 PM, temporary stop closures on Wilson Street, Labrador affected route 713. Use the alternative stop approximately 55m away until further notice.

From 2025-07-18 9:00 PM to 2026-07-18, new late night trips for routes 600 and 616 operate on Friday and Saturday nights from a new stop at Maroochydore Road at Beach Road, with additional stops in Mooloolaba. Security guards are onboard all trips as part of a 12-month trial.

From 2025-08-25 4:00 AM to 2026-02-27 11:59 PM, temporary stop closures affect routes 704, 710, 3352, 3038, and 3042 on Gold Coast Highway at Discovery Drive (Stop ID 300272). Alternative stops include Helensvale station (320914), Lindfield Rd at Helensvale Plaza (300281), and Helensvale Community Centre (300261).

From 2026-01-27 4:00 AM, timetable changes for Route 233 in Townsville may cause buses to arrive earlier or later than usual. Please replan your travel using a date from Tuesday 27 January and check your updated timetable.

From 2025-09-15 4:00 AM to 2026-03-31 11:59 PM, temporary stop closure at Riverway Drive, Mac Court (Stop ID 890472) due to roadworks. Use the alternative stop on Riverway Drive, approximately 70m away.

From 2025-12-05 to 2026-04-10 11:59 PM, temporary stop closures on Mona Street, Whitfield affected routes 172, 181, 182, and 183. Closed stops include Mona St near Crowther St (750558) and Mona St near Draper Pl (750563). Use alternative stops at Woodward Street at Heavey Crescent (750464) and Woodward Street at McManus Street (750465).

From 2025-11-29 to 2026-06-30 9:00 PM, Shorncliffe station is closed for major upgrades, affecting Shorncliffe Line services which will run between Brisbane City and Sandgate station. Alternative transport includes railbus R346 (Sandgate-Shorncliffe) and Route 313 (Sandgate-Shorncliffe) with stops at Sandgate Central, Eagle Terrace, Shorncliffe State School, Saint Patricks College, and Moora Park.

From 2025-10-24 to 2026-02-15 11:59 AM, temporary stop closure on Andrew Road, Greenbank (Stop ID SI:312246) due to electrical works. Affected routes 541, 6043, and 6151. Use the temporary stop approximately 80m away (1 min walk).

From 2025-12-16 8:30 PM to 2025-12-16 11:59 PM, Buranda busway station will be closed for essential tunnel maintenance. Routes 120, 180, 169, 179, 205, 209, 222, and 555 will not stop at Buranda station. Affected stations include Stones Corner and Langlands Park. Alternative stops are available at O'Keefe Street and Old Cleveland Rd locations.

From 2025-12-17 8:30 PM to 2025-12-17 11:59 PM, parts of the Northern busway will be closed due to essential tunnel maintenance, affecting routes M2, 330, 333, and 340. QUT Kelvin Grove and Herston stations will be closed, with alternative stops available for routes 330, 333, and 340. Metro M2 will terminate at Roma Street station.

From 2025-10-31 12:00 AM to 2026-01-31 11:59 PM, temporary stop closures on route 679 affected stops 315215 and 317973 at Cairns Rd at Vermilion Avenue, Griffin and Vermillion Ave near Grandview Pde, Griffin due to roadworks. Alternative stops are available.

From 29/10/2025 1:30 PM until further notice, Flinders Street at Fletcher Street, Townsville City (Stop ID 890343) will be closed for bus stop accessibility. Affected routes 200, 201, 202, 203, 204, 207, and 258 should use alternative stops: Flinders St at Knapp Street (890342) and Flinders St at Blackwood Street (890344).

From 2025-11-10 to 2026-05-31, temporary stop closures affect routes 6702, 6706, 6820, 6824, 6831, 6833, 6860, 6861, and 6871 at Murrumba Downs Shopping Centre on Dohles Rocks Road. Use the alternative stop on Goodrich Road (Stop ID 317934) for access.

From 01/02/2026 4:30 AM to 11:00 AM, temporary stop closures affected routes 250, N250, 271, and 274 at Cleveland station (Stop ID 310063), Shore St at Black Swamp Wetlands, Shore St at RACQ, and other locations due to the Raby Bay Triathlon. Use alternative stops as indicated.

From 2025-11-17 to 2026-03-31 11:59 PM, temporary stop closures on Denmans Camp Road and Totness Street, Scarness affect route 705. Closed stops include 840043 and 840049, with alternative stops at 840102 and 840050.

From 2026-02-18 8:30 PM to 2026-02-18 11:59 PM, parts of the Northern busway will be closed due to essential tunnel maintenance. Routes M2, 330, 333, and 340 will be affected, with QUT Kelvin Grove and Herston stations closed. Alternative stops are available for affected services.

From 2026-02-17 8:30 PM to 2026-02-17 11:59 PM, Buranda busway station closure affects routes 120, 169, 179, 180, 205, 209, 222, and 555. Stations impacted include Buranda busway, Stones Corner, and Langlands Park. Alternative stops are available for some routes.

From 2026-05-26 8:30 PM to 2026-05-26 11:59 PM, Buranda busway station closure affects routes 209, 222, 120, 180, 169, 179, 205, and 555. Services will not stop at Buranda busway station, with alternative stops at O'Keefe Street and revised stops at Stones Corner and Langlands Park stations.

From 2025-12-27 to 2026-02-02, temporary bus stop closures on Charlotte Street, Brisbane City affect routes 171, 176, 181, 186, 332, 344, 384. Services will be relocated to temporary stop 92 on Mary Street during Cross River Rail construction works.
On 2026-01-27, route 50 will begin servicing stop 000105 at William Street near Margaret Street (underneath The Star Brisbane hotel and casino complex).

On 2025-12-09, a minor timetable change affects route TX7 at Coomera station. The first service departs 8:09 AM instead of 8:07 AM to add buffer time between the 8:04 AM Brisbane City train arrival and the TX7 departure. Travelers are advised to replan their journeys for this date.

On 2026-02-23, improved bus services will operate on routes 562, 563, 564, 568, 565, and 582, with route realignments, extended operating hours, and new stops in Bahrs Scrub, Bethania, Meadowbrook, and Holmview. Route 564 and 568 will be replaced by upgraded routes 562/563, while route 582 is renumbered to 580. New stops include Rosella Drv (322392), Bahrs Scrub Rd at Hein Rd (322393), Prangley Rd at Brookhaven Bvd (322395), and others.
From 2026-01-27 4:00 AM to 2026-04-07, Moreton Bay bus services 680, 687, 688, 689, 690, 691 will follow school term timetables, with the next holiday timetables starting on 2026-04-07.

From 2026-01-27 4:00 AM to 2026-04-07, Sunshine Coast bus services 602, 603, 607, 610, 612, 614, 615, 616, 617, 618, 620, 622, 628, 629, 631, 636 return to school term timetables with temporary adjustments affecting the region.
On 2026-01-26, route 535 will begin servicing a new bus stop at Gateway Drive, Elizabeth Drive, Undullah (Logan City).
From 2026-01-21 to 2026-08-15, temporary stop closures on Riverway Drive, Kelso affect route 200. Alternative stops are available for route 200 towards Breakwater ferry terminal and Kelso.

On 2026-01-27 4:00 AM, minor timetable changes affect route 561 with a 3-minute delay to the 7:45am weekday service to Brisbane City. The 561 now departs from Bumstead Road near Judith Street, Crestmead (Stop ID 321129) at 7:48am. No other services are impacted.
On 2025-12-19, ticketing payment issues affect routes 860 and 861 in the Whitsunday region. Single trip payments only; daily and 10-trip tickets unavailable. Pay with debit/credit card or cash.

On 2026-01-27 4:00 AM, a minor timetable change affects route 262, with buses arriving or departing slightly earlier or later than usual. Replan travel using a date from Tuesday 27 January or check updated timetables for affected journeys.

From 2026-02-06 11:30 PM to 2026-02-08 11:59 PM, track closure on Ipswich/Rosewood and Springfield lines. Railbuses will replace trains between Roma Street to Rosewood and Springfield Central stations.

From 2026-02-09 9:30 PM to 2026-02-09 11:59 PM, late night track closure on the Ipswich/Rosewood Line affects stations Darra, Wacol, Gailes, Goodna, Redbank, Riverview, Dinmore, Ebbw Vale, Bundamba, Booval, East Ipswich, and Ipswich. Railbuses will replace trains between Darra and Ipswich station.

From 2026-02-16 9:30 PM to 2026-02-17 11:59 PM, track closures on Ipswich/Rosewood and Springfield lines affected stations including Roma Street, Milton, Corinda, and others, with railbuses replacing trains between Roma Street and Corinda. Bikes and e-scooters are not permitted on railbuses.

From 2026-02-18 9:30 PM to 2026-02-19 11:59 PM, track closures on Beenleigh and Gold Coast lines affected stations including Boggo Road, Kuraby, and others. Railbuses replace trains between Boggo Road and Kuraby station.

From 23/02/2026 9:30 PM to 24/02/2026 11:59 PM, late night track closures on inner-city lines (Airport Line, Beenleigh Line, Cleveland Line, Doomben Line, Gold Coast Line, Ipswich/Rosewood Line, Springfield Line, Ferny Grove Line, Redcliffe Peninsula Line, Shorncliffe Line, Caboolture Line, Sunshine Coast Line) affect services between Albion, Bowen Hills, Fortitude Valley Central, Roma Street, Milton, and South Brisbane. Railbuses replace trains between Bowen Hills and Albion to South Brisbane and Milton stations.

From 2026-02-25 9:30 PM to 2026-02-25 11:59 PM, track closure affects all lines including Caboolture Line, Redcliffe Peninsula Line, Ferny Grove Line, Shorncliffe Line, Sunshine Coast Line, Airport Line, Beenleigh Line, Cleveland Line, Gold Coast Line, Ipswich/Rosewood Line, Springfield Line. Affected stations include Airport line, Eagle Junction, International Airport, Domestic Airport, Inner city, Bowen Hills, Fortitude Valley, Central, Roma Street, Inner north, Northgate, Ferny Grove, and others.

From 2026-02-26 10:15 PM to 2026-02-26 11:59 PM, track closure on Shorncliffe Line, Caboolture Line, and Redcliffe Peninsula Line in Inner north. Railbuses will run between Bowen Hills to Northgate stations during the closure.

From 2026-01-31 4:00 AM to 2026-02-01 11:59 PM, track closure on Caboolture, Redcliffe Peninsula, Shorncliffe, and Sunshine Coast lines. Railbuses will replace trains between Eagle Junction to Gympie North, Shorncliffe, and Kippa Ring stations. Bikes and e-scooters are not permitted on railbuses.

From 2026-02-13 11:00 PM to 2026-02-15 11:59 PM, track closure on Beenleigh and Gold Coast lines. Railbuses will replace trains between Boggo Road and Varsity Lakes stations. Bikes and e-scooters are not permitted on railbuses.

From 2026-02-28 4:00 AM to 2026-03-01 11:59 PM, track closures on inner-city and Southern lines affect Beenleigh Line, Ipswich/Rosewood Line, Springfield Line, Cleveland Line, Gold Coast Line, Airport Line, Caboolture Line, Doomben Line, Ferny Grove Line, Redcliffe Peninsula Line, Shorncliffe Line, and Sunshine Coast Line. Railbuses replace trains between Bowen Hills and Roma Street to Cannon Hill, Banoon, Corinda stations, with restrictions on bikes and e-scooters.

On 2026-01-27 5:00 AM, there will be a minor timetable change for route 555, affecting South East Queensland Bus 555 with possible slight variations in arrival and departure times. Please check the updated timetable for affected journeys.

On 2026-01-27 5:00 AM, minor timetable changes for route 546 may cause slight delays or early arrivals. Replan travel using a date from Tuesday 27 January or check the updated timetable for affected journeys.

From 2026-01-15 12:00 AM to 2026-02-03 4:00 PM, temporary stop closures affected route 463 at Boundary Rd at Campbell Avenue, Wacol (Stop IDs 013108 and 013109). Alternate stops are available for route 463 towards Forest Lake and Goodna.

On 2026-01-26 4:00 AM, route 182 services towards Garden City will start from stop 57/61 on Bapaume Road near Sterculia Avenue under Holland Park West station. Route changes will remove service to Cannes Street and Bapaume Road stops including IDs 002272, 002275, 000573, 010524. Replan travel using updated routes.

From 2026-01-27, Bundaberg Bus routes 621, 622, 670-682 will be operated by Kinetic Bundaberg with no timetable changes. School services include routes between Nolans Pocket, Woongarra SS, Sharon, and Bundaberg North SHS.
On 2026-02-02 4:00 AM, permanent stop closures affected route 902 on Phyllis Street near Anzac Ave in Harristown. Use alternative stops on Glenvale Road.

From 2026-01-27 to 2026-01-30, temporary stop closures affect routes 705, 3104, and 3445 on Main Beach Parade, Main Beach. Closed stops include Main Beach Pde at Main Beach Tourist Park (IDs 300321, 300318) with alternative stops available at Woodroffe Avenue (IDs 300319, 300323).

From 2026-02-07 4:00 AM to 2026-03-01 11:59 PM, track closures on the Shorncliffe Line between Northgate and Sandgate stations for ETCS testing. Timetabled railbuses will replace trains during the closure period, with affected stations including Northgate, Bindha, Banyo, Nudgee, Boondall, North Boondall, Deagon, Sandgate, and Shorncliffe.

From 2026-02-06 6:00 AM to 2026-02-07 12:00 PM, temporary stop closures affect routes 705 and 716 at Esplanade, Hervey Bay due to the Queensland State Schools Triathlon. Alternative stops are available at specified locations.

From 2026-02-03 to 2026-02-04 1:00 AM, the stop on Gold Coast Highway at Twenty Fifth Avenue, Palm Beach (Stop ID 300423) is closed due to construction works. Affected routes 700 and 760 should use alternative stops at Twenty Seventh Avenue and Twenty First Avenue.
On 2026-01-27, temporary stop closures affected routes 19 and 116 at Ipswich Road, Moorooka station. Use alternative stop 38/90 (Stop ID 010396) due to Cross River Rail works upgrades.
On 2026-01-22, permanent stop closures at Annette Kellerman Park, Mermaid Beach affected route 700. Use alternative stops near Tamborine Street for route 700.
From 2026-02-06 8:30 AM to 3:00 PM, temporary stop closures affected route 574 at Springwood Rd at Flinders View (Stop ID 311075). Use the temporary stop approximately 175m away on Springwood Road.

From 2026-02-02 9:00 AM to 2026-02-13 3:30 PM, Gold Coast trains from Ormeau to Varsity Lakes will run eight minutes late between 9:00 AM and 3:30 PM daily, impacting routes 721, 722, 728, 729, 724, 732, 733, 723, 725, 727, Tx7, 704, 710, 714, 715, 716, 717, 718, 725, 727, Tx7, 735, 740, 743, 744, 745, 748, 747, 748, 750, 751, 752, 755, 758, 759, 753, 757, 759, 760, 765 at Ormeau, Coomera, Helensvale, Nerang, Robina, Varsity Lakes, and Pimpama stations. Trains from Varsity Lakes to the city are unaffected.

From 2026-02-09 to 2026-05-01, temporary stop closures on Cooroy Street near Coochin St, Dicky Beach affected routes 600, 607, and school services 5541, 5551, 5702, 5717. Use alternative stops listed in the notice.

From 2026-01-29 8:23 AM, routes 737 and 741 will miss the stop Benowa Rd at Collins Crescent, Benowa (Stop ID 300101) due to emergency works. Other affected stops include Benowa Rd at St Kevins Catholic Primary (320958), Benowa Rd at Sapium Road, Ashmore (300067), and Heeb St at Gold Coast TAFE Ashmore (300081).
On 2026-01-30 4:33 AM, Route 131 towards Raintrees Shopping Centre is missing the stop at Woodward Street and McManus Street, Whitfield due to road works.
On 2026-01-30 12:06 PM, the route 732 to Robina is cancelled due to staff availability, affecting service 752.
On 2026-01-30 12:49 PM, the route 760 to Tweed Heads is cancelled due to staff availability.
On 2026-01-30 11:50 AM, route 404 to The Range was cancelled. This service notice has been resolved.
On 2026-01-30 12:40 PM, route 404 to Kawana is cancelled due to staff availability.
On 2026-01-30 11:43 AM, the route 905 to Darling Heights is delayed up to 18 minutes due to late running of a previous service.
On 2026-01-30 11:43 AM, the route 907 to Darling Heights is delayed up to 23 minutes due to late running of a previous service.
On 2026-01-30, the 11:55am route 616 to Palmview is delayed up to 15 minutes due to late running of a previous service.
On 2026-01-30 11:38 AM, the route 902 to Toowoomba is delayed up to 32 minutes due to mechanical issues affecting Toowoomba Bus 902.
On 2026-01-30 12:05 PM, route 694 to Kippa-Ring is delayed up to 15 minutes due to boarding delays.
On 2026-01-30 12:02 PM, route 902 to Glenvale is delayed up to 15 minutes due to congestion.
On 2026-01-30 11:48 AM, route 907 to Cranley is delayed up to 18 minutes due to congestion.
